## Step 9
Dividing both sides of the equation from step 8 by 2, we find P(C) = 0.52.


## Step 10
Now, using P(PT) = P(C) + 0.16 from step 6 and P(C) = 0.52 from step 9, we find P(PT) = 0.52 + 0.16 = 0.68.

